After enabling, you can BCC a designated email address when emailing your leads/contacts and it will automatically archive and appear in the appropriate activity history subpanel(s). This project provides similar functionality as Email-To-Salesforce.


Available on SugarForge
========================
http://www.sugarforge.org/projects/email-to-sugar
(Documentation is also there)

Usage
=====

Run email_to_sugar.php from a scheduled task in sugar regularly.  
